Tere Mere Yun Beech Me, Kahan Se Aa Gaya Yeh Jahaan, Poochhe Bina Mujhse Agar, Tu Le Chuka Hai Faisla, Kabhi Na Aana Bhale Dobaara, Magar, [Humko Tere Bina Jeena Toh Sikha, Chale Jaana Phir Hai Jaana Jahan] –(2), Thodi Der Pehle Tu Mera Hi Toh Tha, Toh Phir Ab Kyun Mera Nahi, Aisa Kya Hua Jo Badal Gaya Tu, Kyun Mujhpe Bharosa Nahi, Zamaana Poochhega Humse, Bahaana Kya Banayenge, Chhupa Le Aansoo, Nahi Hai Itna, Hunar, [Humko Tere Bina Jeena Toh Sikha, Chale Jaana Phir Hai Jaana Jahan] –(2), Humko Sikha Ke Chale Jaana Jeena, Jeena Sikha Ke Chale Jaana, Jeena Sikha Ke Chale Jaana Jeena, Jeena Sikha Ke Chale Jaana
